      "title": "Extraction aftercare",
      "subject": "Aftercare - Tooth Extraction",
      "body": "Hello {name},\n\nAfter your tooth extraction, please follow these instructions:\n1) Bite firmly on the gauze for 30-45 minutes (change if needed).\n2) Do not rinse/spit for the first 24 hours.\n3) Avoid smoking/alcohol for 48-72 hours.\n4) Soft, cool foods today. Avoid hot and spicy foods.\n5) If bleeding continues: place fresh gauze and apply pressure.\n\nPain and swelling:\n- Use ice pack outside the cheek (10 min on / 10 min off) for the first 6-8 hours.\n- Take medicines as prescribed.\n\nStart gentle warm salt-water rinses after 24 hours (3-4 times/day).\n\nCall us immediately if you have uncontrolled bleeding, fever, or increasing swelling.\n\n- {clinic}",
